content: This is the channel for the SANER Connectathon testing, questions can go to @Keith Boone or @Austin Kreisler

Hello,
Managed to officially register for the Connectathon over the weekend, and pushed the latest codebase to our servers. Please add the following to the list of participants:

Organization: Symptomatic, LLC
Contact: Abigail Watson
Email: abigail@symptomatic.io
Base URL: https://saner.symptomatic.io/baseR4

Hey all! I may be jumping the gun a bit, but do you know if there will be any MeasureReport Capacity examples that will be published prior to the Connectathon with the expanded set of data? I'd like to make sure we're passing on the additional data points correctly.
Hasn't been created, as far as I'm aware. We've got that on this week's agenda. MeasureReports from the last connectathon are available.
